    <item>
      <title>印度拒绝锡克教阴谋报告，抨击加拿大分裂分子</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-30/india-rejects-sikh-plot-report-slams-canada-over-separatists</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度驳回了《华盛顿邮报》的一篇报道，该报道称该国情报机构高级成员批准了杀害一名驻美国锡克教活动人士的阴谋，同时对加拿大锡克教活动中表达的分离主义情绪表示担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-30/india-rejects-sikh-plot-report-slams-canada-over-separatists</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 07:24:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>格鲁吉亚亿万富翁拥王者猛烈抨击西方“战争党”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-30/georgia-s-billionaire-powerbroker-lashes-west-as-the-war-party</link>
      <description><![CDATA[格鲁吉亚执政党的亿万富翁创始人猛烈抨击西方，誓言要通过一项有争议的有关“外国代理人”的法律，该法律引发了大规模抗议，并遭到美国和欧盟的谴责。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-30/georgia-s-billionaire-powerbroker-lashes-west-as-the-war-party</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 07:13:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国将于7月召开推迟举行的党的改革会议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-30/china-to-hold-delayed-party-conclave-focusing-on-reform-in-july</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国国家主席习近平将于 7 月召集党内高级官员召开闭门会议，届时将密切关注世界第二大经济体长期改革的迹象。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-30/china-to-hold-delayed-party-conclave-focusing-on-reform-in-july</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 07:05:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
